keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell's attorneys were in regular contact with SDNY prosecutors from at least July 2019 through 2020.
The contact included meetings at SDNY offices, phone calls, and emails.
The timeline suggests ongoing legal negotiations or discussions prior to Maxwell's arrest in July 2020.
